spec: agent-core.file-index/v1
file: ToolCatalogProviderInterface.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Contract\\Tool\\ToolCatalogProviderInterface"
type: interface
summary: Defines the contract for resolving tool catalogs within the AgentCore framework. Implementations provide a mechanism to retrieve available tools based on a provided context array. This interface abstracts the source of tool definitions to allow for flexible catalog resolution strategies.
methods[1]{method,start,end,limit,symbolLine,symbolColumn,signature}:
